ctu.nengoros.comm.nodeFactory.nativenode.impl

Class RunnableNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • ctu.nengoros.comm.nodeFactory.nativenode.impl.RunnableNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExternalNodeContainer, NativeNodeContainer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UNodeContainer

    public class RunnableNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements NativeNodeContainer
    Class that is able to run external process, read both streams and automatically kill process when a corresponding static variable indicates it. Note: autokiller refers to static variable in the class NengoGrahics
